{"tid":368458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波涉誹謗案　原訟人獲批上訴終院","createTime":"2017-08-21T14:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T16:15:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79e0aedaaf4121dd50481157ba1a421291e4ec62","tid":368458,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】財政司司長陳茂波夫婦涉嫌誹謗案，早前敗訴的漢基國際學校校董盧光漢獲批准上訴至終審法院。<br />\n<br />\n終審法院首席法官馬道立、常任法官鄧國楨和霍兆剛處理上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n代表盧光漢一方指，上訴庭判詞中部分論點有矛盾。陳茂波一方就反駁指，即使上訴庭部分觀點存在疑問，但不可因而推翻所有理據。終審法院聽取雙方陳詞後，批出上訴許可，排期明年三月處理，預計審訊兩日。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立指，終審法院將會處理誹謗的免責條款，是否需要考慮當時人說話的時候有沒有惡意，如果原審法官有誤導陪審團，案件是否需要重審以及日後法官應如何引導陪審團。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波夫婦被指六年前以電郵等，誹謗漢基國際學校校董盧光漢包庇子女考試作弊，盧光漢原審勝訴，但上訴則被判敗訴。"},{"pid":"7db9f3605a84fc912c15820a565e849f8e3ef802","tid":368458,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"留名睇波叔PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c37fb450dd91def5069348c5dddfdab5e38cbb2","tid":368458,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c558c96a0beb7142767accb45485ebea413abcaa","tid":368458,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"又上訴庭出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43d6d2fa0dd4efc4bff7d396ca2864cfd1fe127","tid":368458,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又上訴庭出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係未滲透到終審庭啫"},{"pid":"0ed7ee24912ffd55d30445da2a9331143da4524a","tid":368458,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017